== Romanian ==
===Adverb===
'''oare'''
#An interrogative. Rough English equivalent being "can". 
=== Etymology ===
Disputed. The [[W:Romanian Academy|Romanian Academy]] derives it with some room for other possibilities from Latin ''[[volet]]''. Other linguists hypothesize a substratum origin, pointing to an Albanian equivalent, ''[[vallë]]''.

